text:
College Point Causeway (South 13th Street) west side, between 25th Street (Ninth Ave.) and Graham Court, showing a set of two views from different angles of the home of Captain J. Graham in 1873. At one time it housed Kyle's Institute. The house was demolished in 1924.

1922.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
title: Queens: College Point Causeway - 25th Street & Graham Court
